<h3 style=”text-align:left”><b><u>Vaughan Garner</u></b></h3><img src="1.jpg" align="right" width="375" length="375"/>
<p>Full Name: Vaughan Christopher Garner</p>
<p>Born: June 1, 1988, Shepparton</p>
<p>Nicknames: Vorn, Vangman Grenckx</p>
<p>Batting style: Right-hand bat</p>
<p>Bowling style: Right-arm medium</p>
<p>Fielding position: Point, wicketkeeper</p>
<p>Teams: Shepparton United, Glenroy, Willowfest</p>
<p>Shirt number: 47</p>
